Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚是不是有点瘸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚才脚滑的时候扭到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没事的  只是回家的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  你摸哪儿呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的路上  我们互相都没有说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后希望做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该听她倾诉一下才比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候可能是拯救她的最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肤浅的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我没有发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不会再让你出门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再让你去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你见任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}不需要什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}你只要有我就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这药  来结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}你只要有我在就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能死成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早上好  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不遵守规定  晚上偷偷溜出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  月亮实在是太美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想去享受森林浴  就不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  给我注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行为会影响到我的评价的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对礼弥用这种说法也太过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲  您不用餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  昨天真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然那样打你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是我不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是很感谢父亲您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  能够保护你的就只有我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么穿着制服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过你这段时间就在家里自习的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  你去换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道些什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  关于昨晚的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少年的身份已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紫阳高中的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二丁目的那个寺院住持的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在说降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让他不能再接近礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他「去势」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了复活药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让死去的小巴布喝了下去  你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好歹也是寺院住持的儿子  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧萌路  真是怀疑他的伦理观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道哥他从以前开始就是喜欢僵尸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着恶趣味的大变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟然会做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  轮不到你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  确实我可能是做了件让人恶心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布真的就这样复活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  难道你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布复活了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我确实也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是真的复活什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听吧  那个特殊的像是鼻音的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是正宗的巴布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说  果然那个还是觉得有点怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}巴布…  快点下来吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且眼珠还在发光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  之前感觉更有感情什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是特征没有什么改变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说会有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊  如果真的复活了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像僵尸那样袭击人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能保证被咬的人就不会被变成僵尸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  这种像漫画一样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的敢百分百保证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哥  书包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  今天我跷课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么了  发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷  哥说什么他把巴布复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要再养只别的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦吼  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴布复活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  真是太好太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都很容易就让我抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  直接用手抓会不会有危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子姐姐啊  你不是还有晨练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有作为姐姐  监督千纮的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爬进那种地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  你要爬进去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就被好好的折腾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长啊  根本看不到尽头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这洞到底通到哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股卡住了  爬不过去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巴布是很重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微也在意一下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  千纮你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到出口了  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的…下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  茂木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}一年五班  康孝  性别·帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢棒球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  嗯  只是看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只是看的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才不发育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞这里舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对茂木性骚扰也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究就是个茂木而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  康孝君  不知道你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个果然还是应该是散女的大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  降…降谷君在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找一年级的降谷千纮君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…千…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗  茂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  好像  今天还没来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找…找那家伙有什么事吗  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要被去势了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  刚刚从大小姐的嘴里…  去…去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会这么关心降谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我没说什么奇怪的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君会在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你说礼弥在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  先让她走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后面跟好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  巴布跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸子那家伙也没跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么监督义务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好  快下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃紫阳花的叶子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  这里难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是昨天那家伙逞强爬的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  咦  为什么她在这个时候会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一直去的废弃旅馆里等着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:15:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想因为自己的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而给降谷君添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要去哪里啊  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林浴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话是不是走得有点远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁  难道说那就是礼弥的父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  回去吧  现在回去还能原谅你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很聪明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是散华家的女儿  我的女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  刚才的行为是怎么回事  礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是你的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这并不代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身心都是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这具体是什么样的自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要外出的自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…  恋爱的自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  请等一下  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就今天  就今天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  反正肯定是要见那个叫降谷的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么啊  这脏兮兮的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会过敏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小巴布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不可以碰它  会被弄脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说那之后降谷君把药完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个药其实是已经完成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  回话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…竟然真的死了  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多开不起玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我复活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  我  做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降…谷君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还没让你喝药  为…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团…团一郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降谷…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像约定的那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请负起责任来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添了不少麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过问题解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.42,0:23:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和写这个的人见了面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好的和他聊过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  散华礼弥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话  「普通的…女孩子…」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要看哦萌路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也接受那边的意思了  不会再迷茫了


